sourcesContent: import { Component, Input } from '@angular/core'; import { carouselModule, imageAndTextModule, imagesModule, landingModule, textModule } from "./moduleTemplates"; @Component({ selector: 'app-module-filterer', templateUrl: './module-filterer.component.html', styleUrls: ['./module-filterer.component.css'] }) export class ModuleFiltererComponent { @Input() module: imageAndTextModule | textModule | imagesModule | landingModule | carouselModule = { type: 'carousel', backgroundColour: '', modules: [] } }
